While using `WebView` we have to provide height. Is there any way such that `WebView` will be rendered based on HTML content for it?

Here are my lines of code :

```
 <View style={{flex: 1, flexDirection:'column'}}>
       <WebView
      originWhitelist={['*']}
      scalesPageToFit 
      startInLoadingState = {true}
      style = {[this.props.style,{flex : 1,borderWidth: 1, height: '100%'}]}
      mixedContentMode="always"
      automaticallyAdjustContentInsets={false}
      source = {this.props.isHTML ? {html :htmlText} : {uri : this.props.uri}}
      />   
      </View> 
```
